---------------------------------------------
Javelin with Piercer Feat - Nested Macros (Only works as part of nested Macro; First Macro, AttackType, contains the nesting query)
---------------------------------------------
Javelin-Piercer-Str-AttackType
?{Attack Type?|Standard,%{Selected|Javelin-Piercer-Str-Standard-Nested} |Advantage,%{Selected|Javelin-Piercer-Str-Advantage-Nested} |Disadvantage,%{Selected|Javelin-Piercer-Str-Disadvantage-Nested} |Double Advantage,%{Selected|Javelin-Piercer-Str-Advantage2-Nested} |Double Disadvantage,%{Selected|Javelin-Piercer-Str-Disadvantage2-Nested} |Triple Advantage,%{Selected|Javelin-Piercer-Str-Advantage3-Nested} |Triple Disadvantage,%{Selected|Javelin-Piercer-Str-Disadvantage3-Nested}} 
---------------------------------------------
Javelin-Piercer-Str-Standard-Nested
&{template:default&#125; {{name=Melee/Ranged Attack - Javelin&#125;&#125; {{Description=*@{Selected|character_name} makes a Javelin attack at a target within range (Melee/30'/120')*&#125;&#125; [[ [[ [[1d6!cf<1cs>6 [Weapon Dice]]] [Weapon Dice] + [[@{Selected|global_damage_mod_roll}]] [Global Dice Mods] ]] [Total Dice] + [[ [[@{Selected|Strength_mod} [Str]]] [Str] + [[@{Selected|global_attack_mod}]] [Global Static Mods] ]] [Total Static] ]] {{Weapon=$[[0]] Piercing&#125;&#125; {{Dice Mods=$[[1]] varies&#125;&#125; {{Static=$[[3]] Piercing + $[[4]] Varies&#125;&#125; {{Dice Total=$[[2]] ***Dice Damage*** &#125;&#125; {{Static Total=$[[6]] ***Static Damage*** &#125;&#125; {{Total=$[[7]] **Total Damage** &#125;&#125; {{Piercer Hit=Once per turn, when you hit a creature with an attack that deals piercing damage, you can reroll one of the attack's damage dice, and you must use the new roll. &#125;&#125; {{Piercer Crit= On a critical - deal an additional [[1d6cf<0cs>100]] Piercing&#125;&#125;
---------------------------------------------
