Javelin with Magic Weapon in Offhand - Nested Macros (Only works as part of nested Macro; First Macro, AttackType, contains the nesting query)
---------------------------------------------
Javelin-Str-MW-Offhand-AttackType
?{Attack Type?|Standard,%{Selected|Javelin-Str-MW-Offhand-Standard-Nested} |Advantage,%{Selected|Javelin-Str-MW-Offhand-Advantage-Nested} |Disadvantage,%{Selected|Javelin-Str-MW-Offhand-Disadvantage-Nested} |Double Advantage,%{Selected|Javelin-Str-MW-Offhand-Advantage2-Nested} |Double Disadvantage,%{Selected|Javelin-Str-MW-Offhand-Disadvantage2-Nested} |Triple Advantage,%{Selected|Javelin-Str-MW-Offhand-Advantage3-Nested} |Triple Disadvantage,%{Selected|Javelin-Str-MW-Offhand-Disadvantage3-Nested}}
---------------------------------------------
